General Information

Enriched ROSEHIP Moisturising body oil

Warnings

Store below 30C. Not to be taken orally. Keep out of reach of children.

Common Uses

Organic ROSEHIP enriched with Vitamin C, Antioxidants and Essential Fatty Acids to nourish and moisturise total body visibly improving skin tone

High in vital Essential Fatty Acids, and one of the best natural sources of Vitamin E, our Organic Rosehip oil helps to improve the appearance of fine lines, scars, sun spots and stretch marks for hydrated, supple skin.

Produced without heat or chemicals to ensure optimum concentration of all the natural nutrients

Ingredients

Organic Rosehip Oil (Rosa Canina Fruit Oil), Sunflower Oil (Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil), Sweet Almond Oil (Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil), Grape Seed Oil (Vitis Vinifera See Oil), Natural Vitamin E Oil (Tocopherol)

Directions

Use daily as an all over BODY and FACE MOISTURISER
